<title>UK: BZW sets warrants on Pan European stock basket.</title>
<headline>BZW sets warrants on Pan European stock basket.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-05-13</dateline>
<text>
<p>BZW Warrants Ltd has issued one million European-style call warrants on a Pan European stock basket, lead manager BZW Deutschland said.</p>
<p>The basket consists of share of Hoechst AG, SAP AG, Bayerische Motoren-Werke AG, Novartis AG, Nestle SA, Zurich Reinsurance Centre, ABB AG, HSBC Holdings, Glaxo Wellcome Plc, British Petroleaum Co, Lloyds TSB Group Plc, Carrefour Supermarch SA, Total SA, Cie Gnrale des Eaux, AXA-UAP, Ericsson, Internationale Nederlanden Groep NV, Philips Electronics NV and Elsevier NV. One basket is controlled by 100 warrants.</p>
<p> STRIKE PRICE    62,700 DEM		ISSUE PRICE  28.5 DEM</p>
<p> MATURITY DATE   12.NOV.98		 PAYDATE	03.JUN.97</p>
<p> LISTING	   LUX			 MIN EXER LOT 1</p>
<p>SPOT REFERENCE  57,000 DEM</p>
<p>--Reuter London Newsroom +44 171 542 7658</p>
